webpackJsonp([48693423600885],{623:function(a,n){a.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<h3>Directory Icons and Program Badges</h3>\n<p>The Directory page now includes pink and purple lightning icons to highlight programs that are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fast to respond with a first response in &#x3C;48 hours on average</li>\n<li>Fast to award by giving a bounty &#x3C;14 days after submission</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We also include a <i>Managed</i> badge to identify programs that are managed by HackerOne.\n\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/sep_2017-6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15-52fba.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 118.14882032667877%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="sep_2017"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/sep_2017-6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/sep_2017-6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15-67829.png 125w,\n/static/sep_2017-6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/sep_2017-6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/sep_2017-6315cb2e5a364cc443e62a68ea0fff15-52fba.png 551w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>Paying out Bounties via the API</h3>\n<p>Organizations now have the ability to payout and suggest bounties and swag using their internal systems via the API. You can view the API documentation for this <a href="https://api.hackerone.com/docs/v1#/reports/bounties">here</a>.</p>\n<h3>Slack Integration 2.0</h3>\n<p>We\'ve revamped our Slack integration so that programs can have:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Granular notification filtering</li>\n<li>Support for multiple channels</li>\n<li>Notifications when a username is mentioned\n\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/aug_2017_2-6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e-17908.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 40.49930651872399%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="aug_2017_2"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/aug_2017_2-6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/aug_2017_2-6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e-67829.png 125w,\n/static/aug_2017_2-6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/aug_2017_2-6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/aug_2017_2-6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/aug_2017_2-6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/aug_2017_2-6a3d8b3b17b3d6f7bd7f5d7ffb70bb6e-17908.png 1442w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Read our <a href="https://www.hackerone.com/blog/slack-integration-update-2">blog post</a> and learn how to <a href="/programs/slack-integration.html">set up Slack integration</a>.</p>\n<h3>Bounty Splitting</h3>\n<p>We now enable programs to have this feature that enables hackers to split bounties with other hackers that helped them find the vulnerability. </p>',frontmatter:{path:"/changelog/2017/august",title:"August 2017"}}},pathContext:{}}}});
